; Test value sorting and comparison with expression types
; Exercises value.cc is_less_than for AMOUNT with different commodities
; (compare_by_commodity for cross-commodity amount comparison)

2024/01/01 European trip
    Expenses:Travel    500 EUR
    Assets:Cash       -500 EUR

2024/01/02 US purchase
    Expenses:Shopping    $200.00
    Assets:Cash         $-200.00

2024/01/03 UK purchase
    Expenses:Shopping    150 GBP
    Assets:Cash         -150 GBP

test reg --sort amount Expenses
24-Jan-02 US purchase           Expenses:Shopping           $200.00      $200.00
24-Jan-01 European trip         Expenses:Travel             500 EUR      $200.00
                                                                         500 EUR
24-Jan-03 UK purchase           Expenses:Shopping           150 GBP      $200.00
                                                                         500 EUR
                                                                         150 GBP
end test
